modShortDescription: Radiated vultures do not have radiated texture in the vanilla game. This mod adds radiated texture to the radiated vultures.
modDescription:
Radiated vultures do not have radiated [texture](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-zombie-textures/) in the vanilla game. This mod adds radiated texture to the radiated vultures.

## Changelog

**v1.1:** Fixed a bug with the vulture texture.

**[Download](http://www.mediafire.com/file/ludy9kasf6d1kyd/GK_Texture_Vulture_Radiated_A19.rar/file)** for A19  
**[Download](http://www.mediafire.com/file/vidyffdlbpyhf3j/GK_Texture_Vulture_Radiated.rar/file)** for A18

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/20168-gouki%C2%B4s-a19-modlets/).
